# This directory holds the bundled pdfium dynamic library for the PDF → Images
# feature. The library itself is gitignored and fetched by scripts/fetch-pdfium.sh
# (run it once per clone; release CI runs it automatically before bundling).
#
# This placeholder keeps the directory present in a fresh checkout so that
# tauri-build's bundle.resources existence check (which runs on every
# cargo build/check/clippy/test, not just `tauri build`) passes without the
# binary. Without it, all Rust compilation fails with:
#   resource path `resources/pdfium` doesn't exist
